167
00:08:49,059 --> 00:08:50,799
We'll start with shelling out.

168
00:08:51,179 --> 00:08:52,539
Alright, so to shell out.

169
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:55,360
So when you shell out, you pay for something.

170
00:08:55,360 --> 00:09:00,700
Alright, but this gives you the sensation that you are, that you don't really want to pay.

171
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,240
You're a bit unhappy about it.

172
00:09:02,779 --> 00:09:04,840
Right, so you want to shell out your money.

