176
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,419
Example two.

177
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:27,720
I really want those shoes, but I can't really afford to shell out four hundred dollars.

178
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:30,700
Example three.

179
00:09:32,019 --> 00:09:33,700
I can't believe it.

180
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,299
Ella shelled out the eight hundred bucks for the tickets.

