00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,940
Are you trying to get our meal comped again?

215
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,179
What do you mean?

216
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:28,059
We are paying for this and I'm shelling out my hard-earned bucks.

217
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:30,059
I expect value from money.

